developer_understanding_on_working: The configuration code is a method that returns the user agent's alternate style-sheet title. It first checks if the alternate style-sheet title is stored in the hints map, if not, it falls back to the super class method to get the alternate style-sheet title.
developer_understanding_on_triggering_fr: The configuration is triggered whenever the getAlternateStyleSheet() method is called in the system.
developer_understanding_on_size_impact: The impact of the ALTERNATE_STYLESHEET configuration option is minimal, as it only affects the user agent's alternate style-sheet title.
